{"_path":"/maps/_product/docs/dovetail","_dir":"docs","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Dovetail","description":"定性研究证据链与洞察管理：将访谈与主题化洞察集中管理、可追溯地关联至产品假设与ROI，强化定性数据在决策中的作用。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"brief"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Brief"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dovetail 平台解决管理碎片化定性研究数据的长期挑战。它为用户访谈、转写与洞察提供集中式存储库，将原始数据转化为可结构化、可分析的资产。我们发现在产品发现工作流中它极具价值，尤其用于建立证据链：把客户引述与归纳主题直接关联到产品假设与ROI估算。由此，Dovetail 强化了定性数据在产品决策中的作用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"来源：技术雷达"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"details"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Details"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"背景与现状"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"背景与现状"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定性研究产出（录音/视频、转写、便签、主题、结论）常分散在多工具中，难以复用与追溯。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"产品探索需要“证据到决策”的可审计链路，以支撑假设验证、ROI 估算与对外说明。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"传统做法依赖手工整理（文档/表格/知识库），在规模化、跨团队协作时易失真和丢失上下文。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"问题与风险"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"问题与风险"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"证据不可追溯：难以从结论回溯到原始引述与访谈上下文，影响可信度与复核效率。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"洞察难结构化：主题、编码口径不统一，复用与查询成本高。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"决策“黑箱化”：缺少证据链支撑时，假设与ROI估算说服力不足。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全与合规：涉及个人信息与敏感业务线索，权限与脱敏若处理不善，风险累积。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"模式与原理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模式与原理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"核心抽象与角色"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心抽象与角色"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"证据与洞察分层：原始素材（录音/转写）→ 编码/标签 → 主题 → 洞察 → 决策/假设。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"关系可追溯：客户引述、归纳主题与产品假设、ROI 估算形成链式关联。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"角色协作：研究者负责采集与编码，产品/设计负责假设与机会评估，工程/数据协同验证与落地。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"工作机制典型流水线"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工作机制（典型流水线）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"采集与转写：导入访谈媒体并自动/半自动转写。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"编码与主题化：基于标签/代码本统一抽象典型需求、痛点与动机。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"洞察沉淀：将主题整合为结论项，标注证据来源与置信度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"证据链绑定：洞察关联到具体产品假设、待办、ROI 估算与评审记录。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"查询与复核：按主题、用户画像、功能域等维度检索，快速回溯到原话片段。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"对比与演进"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对比与演进"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"旧做法-vs-新模式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旧做法 vs 新模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旧：分散文档/表格/笔记工具，弱结构、弱查询、弱追溯。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新：集中仓库与统一编码体系，支持纵深检索与端到端证据链。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"演进方向"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"演进方向"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与交付侧集成：将洞察链接至需求管理与路线图，形成从发现到交付的闭环。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与定量互证：把定性主题映射到埋点/实验指标，构建“定性-定量”相互印证的证据网。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"系统影响"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"系统影响"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"架构与数据治理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"架构与数据治理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"引入统一的“研究知识层”，需要稳定的模式与标签治理（命名、合并、废弃策略）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对存储与权限模型提出更精细的需求（项目隔离、字段级脱敏、外部共享控制）。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"工程效率与协作"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工程效率与协作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缩短从素材到可用洞察的周期，减少重复访谈与决策拉扯。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"决策透明度提升，有利于评审与跨部门对齐。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"安全与合规"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全与合规"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"必须明确数据驻留、PII/敏感信息处理与访问审计；对外分享需模板化脱敏。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"适用边界"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"适用边界"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更适合：中大型产品线、持续性用户研究、需为路线图与ROI提供证据链的团队。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"谨慎使用：纯定量驱动、需求简单的小团队；或数据出境/本地化要求极严、难以合规时。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不适用：仅一次性调研、无持续沉淀需求的场景。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"落地建议"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"落地建议"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"前置条件"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前置条件"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"明确研究工作流与“从证据到假设/ROI”的产出模板。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立最小可用代码本（标签体系），定义命名规范与治理机制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"明确敏感数据处理策略（脱敏、留存周期、访问控制）。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"试点路径契合-trial-阶段"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"试点路径（契合 Trial 阶段）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"选择1条产品线、2–3个研究项目作为试点；限定范围与成功标准。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"打通最小闭环：访谈导入→转写→编码→主题→洞察→链接到需求/假设与ROI记录。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与现有工具集成：将洞察链接到需求系统（如工单/路线图），用双向链接保留追溯。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"评估指标：可复用洞察比例、回溯平均用时、决策通过率、重复研究减少率。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"风险与对策"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"风险与对策"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"标签漂移与口径不一：设立编码评审与定期清理（合并/废弃），提供示例库。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自动转写误差：设置信心阈值与抽样人工校对；对关键证据片段强制复核。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"成本与供给侧约束：控制席位与项目并发量，分层授权与阶段性归档。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"供应商锁定：导出策略（原文与标注）、保留关键结构化字段的中性格式。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"实施要点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实施要点"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"与产品决策的耦合"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与产品决策的耦合"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在评审模板中要求“洞察-引述-主题-假设-ROI”的链路字段为必填。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为关键路线图项配置证据看板，确保高优先级事项可一键追溯到原话。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"与度量与质量的结合"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与度量与质量的结合"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为洞察设置信任度与样本覆盖度标记；将“定性洞察被复用次数”纳入研究资产指标。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将负向证据（与假设相反的引述）同样记录，避免“只收集支持证据”的偏差。"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"brief","depth":2,"text":"Brief"},{"id":"details","depth":2,"text":"Details","children":[{"id":"背景与现状","depth":3,"text":"背景与现状"},{"id":"问题与风险","depth":3,"text":"问题与风险"},{"id":"模式与原理","depth":3,"text":"模式与原理"},{"id":"对比与演进","depth":3,"text":"对比与演进"},{"id":"系统影响","depth":3,"text":"系统影响"},{"id":"适用边界","depth":3,"text":"适用边界"},{"id":"落地建议","depth":3,"text":"落地建议"},{"id":"实施要点","depth":3,"text":"实施要点"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_product:docs:dovetail.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_product/docs/dovetail.md","_stem":"6.maps/_product/docs/dovetail","_extension":"md"}